message: Hey guys! I am still looking for a male sublease for my apartment at the 4th St. Co-op beginning in January of 2018.  I live with four other awesome guys in a 3 bedroom, 3 bath apartment.  You would be sharing a bedroom with one other guy.  Rent is $460/month plus utilities which are usually $20/month.  If you know anyone who is interested, please send me a message!
